title: Desantis = MAGA Terminator, Let Cereal Die? 6.23.22
itunes:title: Desantis = MAGA Terminator, Let Cereal Die? 6.23.22
description:
Jack and Miles are joined by writer, comedian, and baldness-advocate Kenny DeForest to talk Coupchella (still), former friends saying "I don't know her" to Trump, the fall of Cereal and plenty more! 

  1. Ron Johnson Squirms
  2. Can Ron DeSantis Displace Donald Trump?
  3. DeSantis Declines to Ask Trump for Endorsement
  4. Dr Oz Drops Trump Branding
  5. We Can't Let Cereal Die

LISTEN: RSCO - Piano Ting
